<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idb82f0942-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea" identifier="/us/usc/t5/s4522"><num value="4522">§ 4522.</num><heading> General provision</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">An award under this subchapter is in addition to the basic pay of the recipient.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idb82f0943-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/101/509/tV/s529/tIV/s408/a">Pub. L. 101–509, title V, § 529 [title IV, § 408(a)]</ref>, <date date="1990-11-05">Nov. 5, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/1427">104 Stat. 1427</ref>, 1467.)</sourceCredit>
