<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="idb82f0945-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="idb82f0946-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective <date date="1992-01-01">Jan. 1, 1992</date>, see section 529 [title IV, § 408(d)] of <ref href="/us/pl/101/509">Pub. L. 101–509</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t5/s4521">section 4521 of this title</ref>.</p>
